SUMMARY:[Hike - Intermediate] 10Km Fast Pace - Heber Down - Whitby
DESCRIPTION:GTA Hiking & Stuff\nHeber Down Conservation!\n\nThis is a **fa
 st-paced** intermediate hike (**Going between 4.5-5km/hr**) with few stops
 . The beginning will be flat with the paved sections\, and we will be goin
 g into the back trails\, where there will be mud. We will cover about 10km
  in 2 hours\, **with minimal breaks**.\n\n**Not a beginner hike!**\n\n**TH
 IS HIKE STARTS AT 9:05am**\n\nBring a water bottle and dress for the weath
 er.\n\nParts of the trail can get muddy from the snow melting. Be prepared
 .\n\nWe are going to meet at the Old Cullen Gardens parking lot.\nIntersec
 tion Cochrane & Taunton.\n\nGo to the back of the parking lot near the new
  Pickleball courts. The path starts to the left of the picnic shelter.\n\n
 **Hike leaves promptly at 9:05am**\n\n**LEGAL DISCLAIMER AND LIABILITY INF
 ORMATION:**\n\nBy RSVP'ing and paying the event fee (if applicable)\, you 
